{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_network_transmit_packets\", \"pod_network_receive_packets\", \"pod_memory_working_set_bytes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_memory_working_set_bytes从2359.1降至0，表明Pod发生重启\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-0内存使用量归零，符合Pod重启特征\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"网络基础设施\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个服务的pod_network_transmit_packets和pod_network_receive_packets同时降为0，表明网络连接普遍中断\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice、frontend、checkoutservice等服务的网络传输包数全部归零\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage异常，可能是网络故障导致的连锁反应\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis-cart-0 CPU使用率异常\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**验证理由**：Trace数据明确支持该假设。网络层面故障（多个服务网络指标归零）和adservice-0 Pod重启（内存归零）同时发生，且时间窗口完全吻合，这表明网络故障可能是触发Pod重启的直接原因。"}
